          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_a70cc8d7-7732-43d0-a1df-5276ef03c51f.jpg",
            "text": "<p>While there are no hard and fast rules, it’s important to see how you can use your face shape to decide the best nose pin for you.. If you have a round face, opt for angular or vertical designs such as<strong> nose studs for women</strong>. They look sleek and balance the features. If you’ve a square face, you’ll love designs with curved or rounded sides. They will soften your defined angles and enhance your feminine look. If you’re blessed with an oval shape, you can choose almost any shape - circular hoops or tiny floral motifs. <strong>Nose rings</strong> are versatile and suit everyone, but you can select<strong> nose rings for nose types </strong>to accentuate your features. Choose <strong>nose studs </strong>that are tiny if you have a petite nose to balance the features. <strong>Nose pins for small nose </strong>can also be tiny floral motifs that do not overpower the look. For a broader nose, choose a clustered or geometric design that draws the attention to craftsmanship rather than to the width of the nose. </p>",
